{"title":"战疫魔","authors":["孙轶青"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":5,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"战疫魔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙轶青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只缘非典害人生，奋起反击动刀兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天道恶行须恶报，纸船送汝上锅烹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇斗疫魔气概雄，白衣战士建殊功。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舍生救死诚堪敬，举国啧啧赞美声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前瘟疫大流行，田野荒芜尸骨横。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"科技今能医百病，消除灾害保康宁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公仆身先战火中，红旗猎猎镇妖风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华夏共振青云志，高奏凯歌响太空。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":14,"page_end":14}